short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple UI for generating Kubernetes pull secrets

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension makes it easy to create ImagePullSecrets for Kubernetes in your browser.

Popular image registries are included by default, custom ones can easily be added and saved for later. Simply type in the authentication credentials, copy, paste, done.
